          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The cross section for the reaction 2H(gamma,p)n has",
                " been measured at laboratory photon energies",
                " Egamma = 133 - 158 MeV and c.m. angles between 30 and",
                " 150 degr. The reaction was induced by the tagged",
                " bremsstrahlung photon beam incident on a liquid",
                " deuterium target.",
                "There is now reasonable agreement between recent",
                " measurements in this energy region and the overall",
                " data set now defines the cross section sufficiently",
                " well to provide a test of current models of the",
                " reaction."
              ]
            }
          ],
